Interface Fields.Filter

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Predicate<Field>
    Enclosing class:
    Fields
    Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public static interface Fields.Filter
extends Predicate<Field>
    Provides some predefined filters for Fields.
